%2F1710614655620534296%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehis%20official%20account%20on%20X%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20days%20later%2C%20Modi%20reiterated%20the%20sentiment%20when%20Netanyahu%20called%20him%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20expressed%20deep%20condolences%20and%20sympathy%20for%20those%20killed%20and%20wounded%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20and%20conveyed%20that%20people%20of%20India%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%20in%20this%20difficult%20hour%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20Indian%20government%20readout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20thank%20Prime%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnetanyahu%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40netanyahu%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20phone%20call%20and%20providing%20an%20update%20on%20the%20ongoing%20situation.%20People%20of%20India%20stand%20firmly%20with%20Israel%20in%20this%20difficult%20hour.%20India%20strongly%20and%20unequivocally%20condemns%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%20and%20manifestations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1711669988116050142%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2010%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20stated%20that%20India%20%E2%80%9Cstrongly%20and%20unequivocally%20condemns%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%20and%20manifestations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20PM%20also%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20Indian%20citizens%20in%20Israel%2C%20to%20which%20Netanyahu%20gave%20full%20support.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20like%20his%20earlier%20remarks%2C%20the%20omissions%20were%20also%20the%20same.%20There%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20militant%20group%20by%20name.%20More%20significantly%2C%20India%20did%20not%20call%20for%20a%20cessation%20of%20conflict%20or%20the%20need%20for%20restraint%2C%20which%20it%20had%20done%20in%20previous%20years%20at%20times%20of%20rising%20violence%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-countries-across-the-world-reacted-to-hamas-attack-and-israel-palestine-war%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20besides%20the%20US%20and%20Western%20allies%20asserting%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20defend%2C%20have%20not%20only%20condemned%20the%20terror%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20but%20also%20called%20for%20exercising%20maximum%20restraint.%20These%20include%20Arab%20countries%20like%20the%20UAE%2C%20Jordan%20and%20Egypt%2C%20which%20have%20diplomatic%20ties%20with%20Israel%2C%20as%20well%20as%20major%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20South%20like%20Brazil%2C%20China%20and%20Indonesia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJapan%2C%20was%20perhaps%20the%20only%20G-7%20member%2C%20which%20not%20only%20condemned%20the%20attack%20but%20also%20called%20on%20all%20parties%20%E2%80%9Cto%20exercise%20maximum%20restrain%E2%80%9D.%20Japanese%20Prime%20Minister%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkishida230%2Fstatus%2F1710912119330517151%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFumio%20Kishida%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20also%20stated%20that%20Tokyo%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20concerned%20about%20a%20number%20of%20casualties%20in%20Gaza%20as%20well%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20India%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20which%20had%20clear%20bipartisan%20support%2C%20there%20are%20sharper%20differences%20among%20Indian%20political%20parties%20in%20their%20initial%20reaction%20to%20the%20escalating%20violence.%3C