v%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20birth%20anniversary%2C%20Qureshi%20highlighted%20the%20lack%20of%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20Muslims%20in%20sectors%20like%20the%20police%2C%20defence%20forces%2C%20and%20banks.%20He%20challenged%20political%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20to%20recognise%20that%20Muslims%20are%20not%20bound%20to%20thoughtlessly%20follow%20commands.%20Qureshi%20emphasised%20the%20pressing%20issues%20faced%20by%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20including%20attacks%20on%20their%20businesses%2C%20places%20of%20worship%2C%20and%20homes%2C%20leaving%20their%20children%20orphaned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20state%20election%2C%20Qureshi%E2%80%99s%20words%20have%20fuelled%20concerns%20among%20Muslim%20leaders%20and%20the%20general%20Muslim%20workers%20within%20the%20Congress.%20Sensing%20that%20their%20aspirations%20to%20contest%20elections%20have%20become%20unattainable%2C%20many%20feel%20excluded%20from%20party%20discussions%20amid%20Hindutva%E2%80%99s%20growing%20influence%20and%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20perceived%20alignment%20with%20at%20least%20a%20so-called%20soft%20version%20of%20it.%20This%20sentiment%20of%20disillusionment%20and%20alienation%20underscores%20the%20complex%20political%20landscape%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20local%20Congress%20worker%20from%20Rajogarh%2C%20Raja%20Mian%2C%20voiced%20his%20frustration%2C%20stating%20that%20Muslim%20party%20workers%20are%20not%20even%20invited%20to%20party%20meetings.%20This%20exclusion%20has%20led%20them%20to%20feel%20undervalued%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20approach%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20which%20also%20appears%20indifferent%20to%20securing%20Muslim%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20abandon%20the%20idea%20of%20contesting%20elections%2C%20we%20grasp%20that%20we%20stand%20no%20chance%20amidst%20the%20Hindutva%20surge%20and%20the%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20inclination%20to%20align%20with%20it%20before%20the%20polls.%20But%20what%E2%80%99s%20disheartening%20is%20that%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20even%20welcomed%20to%20the%20party%20meetings%20or%20election%20gatherings.%20It%E2%80%99s%20as%20if%20we%20hold%20no%20value%20for%20the%20party.%20Much%20like%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20disregard%20Muslim%20votes%2C%20assuming%20we%20will%20naturally%20gravitate%20toward%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raja%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sentiments%20underscore%20a%20broader%20discontent%20within%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20raising%20critical%20questions%20about%20their%20representation%20and%20recognition%20within%20political%20spheres%2C%20particularly%20as%20the%20state%20gears%20up%20for%20an%20electoral%20battle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F18143119%2FSIRSA-GENERAL-PICS.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F18143119%2FSIRSA-GENERAL-PICS.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F18143119%2FSIRSA-GENERAL-PICS-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F18143119%2FSIRSA-GENERAL-PICS-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-406264%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20flags.%20Photo%3A%20Bazil%20Ashrafi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%202011%20census%2C%20Muslims%20constitute%20approximately%206.57%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20state%20is%20home%20to%20about%205%20million%20Muslims%2C%20with%20over%20a%20million%20residing%20in%20more%20than%2019%20districts.%20Additionally%2C%20Muslims%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20assembly%20constituencies%2C%20including%20key%20ones%2C%20like%20Indore-1%2C%20Indore-3%2C%20Ujjain%2C%20Jabalpur%2C%20Khandwa%2C%20Ratlam%2C%20Javara%2C%20Gwalior%2C%20Shajapur%2C%20Mandla%2C%20Neemuch%2C%20Mahidpur%2C%20Mandsaur%2C%20Indore-5%2C%20Nasrullaganj%2C%20Ichhawar%2C%20Ashta%2C%20and%20Ujjain%20South%2C%20owing%20to%20their%20substantial%20presence.%20This%20demographic%20factor%20underscores%20their%20political%20influence%20in%20these%20regions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENonetheless%2C%20Muslim%20political%20representation%20in%20the%20state%20has%20experienced%20a%20substantial%20decline%20over%20the%20years.%20At%20its%20peak%2C%20Muslim%20representation%20was%20at%207%25%20in%201962%20when%20leaders%20like%20Shakir%20Ali%20Khan%20from%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20were%20also%20elected.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%20only%20two%20Muslim%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Assembly%3A%20Arif%20Aqueel%20from%20Bhopal%20North%20and%20Arif%20Masood%20from%20Bhopal%20Central.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Congress%20is%20yet%20to%20release%20its%20list%20of%20candidates%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20included%20a%20single%20Muslim%20name%20in%20its%20lists%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhat-it-means-indian-muslim-today%5C%22%3EWhat%20It%20Means%20to%20Be%20an%20Indian%20Muslim%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20not%20every%20Muslim%20leader%20within%20the%20Congress%20is%20on%20the%20same%20page.%20Abbas%20Hafeez%2C%20vice%20chairman%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20media%20department%20in%20the%20state%2C%20believes%20that%20this%20debate%20around%20representation%20is%20not%20going%20to%20take%20Muslims%20anywhere%20and%2C%20at%20a%20moment%20like%20this%2C%20when%20the%20country%20is%20going%20through%20unprecedented%20challenges%2C%20Muslim%20leaders%20should%20take%20off%20their%20blinkers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSee%20tickets%20are%20distributed%20based%20on%20the%20winnability%20chances%20of%20the%20candidates%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20surveys%20conducted%20by%20the%20party.%20The%20party%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20look%20at%20Muslim%20and%20Hindu%20names%2C%20it%20looks%20at%20the%20winnability%20of%20a%20candidate.%20But%20it%20ensures%20that%20the%20candidate%20is%20secular%20and%20will%20take%20everyone%20along.%20Also%2C%20the%20Muslim%20leaders%20who%20are%20complaining%20now%20should%20introspect%20on%20what%20they%20did%20while%20holding%20portfolios%20in%20the%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abbas%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20asserted%20that%20Muslim%20leaders%20should%20focus%20on%20defeating%20communal%20forces%20in%20the%20state%20rather%20than%20placing%20vague%20demands%20of%20representation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Rajneesh%20Agarwal%2C%20on%20the%20question%20of%20Muslim%20representation%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fmadhya-pradesh-polls-38-lakh-muslim-voters-only-4-candidates%5C%22%3Equoted%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20party%20distributes%20tickets%20based%20on%20the%20winning%20ability%20of%20a%20candidate%20and%20majoritarian%20views.%20And%20Muslim%20candidates%20hardly%20get%20in%20with%20the%20majoritarian%20view.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDisillusionment%20of%20Muslim%20voters%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20situation%20has%20not%20only%20affected%20Muslim%20political%20leaders%20and%20workers%20but%20there%20is%20also%20a%20growing%20disenchantment%20among%20Muslim%20voters%20regarding%20the%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Jahangirpura%20locality%20of%20Bhopal%2C%20which%20is%20predominantly%20a%20Muslim%20area%2C%20there%20is%20an%20eerie%20silence%20and%20lack%20of%20electoral%20activity%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%20past.%20Showkat%20Ali%20Jahan%2C%20a%2044-year-old%20food%20joint%20owner%2C%20believes%20that%20Muslims%20are%20getting%20disillusioned%20by%20the%20election%20process%20owing%20to%20the%20increasing%20isolation%20and%20sidelining%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20these%20streets%20were%20filled%20with%20party%20flags%2C%20posters%2C%20and%20banners%20ahead%20of%20any%20elections.%20But%20now%2C%20our%20interest%20in%20the%20elections%20is%20waning%2C%20especially%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20seem%20to%20be%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20coin.%20While%20BJP%20has%20always%20been%20a%20pro-Hindutva%20party%2C%20now%20Congress%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-in-quest-for-power-is-congress-ready-to-compromise-on-secularism%5C%22%3Etrying%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20it%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20this%20situation%2C%20who%20cares%20about%20us%20when%20the%20entire%20political%20discourse%20is%20against%20us%3F%20The%20challenge%20for%20us%20is%20survival%20now%2C%20on%20socio-economic%20fronts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Showkat%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20living%20conditions%20in%20the%20Jahangirabad%20locality%20mirror%20those%20of%20other%20Muslim%20ghettos%20in%20the%20country%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20lack%20of%20civic%20amenities%2C%20insufficient%20infrastructure%2C%20limited%20educational%20institutions%2C%20and%20gross%20municipal%20negligence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERafiqa%20Bano%2C%20a%2061-year-old%20resident%20who%20has%20always%20lived%20in%20Jahangirpura%2C%20believes%20that%20her%20vote%20is%20not%20significant%20to%20anyone.%20Nevertheless%2C%20she%20hopes%20for%20a%20Congress%20victory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20prominent%20leaders%20used%20to%20visit%20our%20neighbourhoods%2C%20make%20promises%2C%20and%20seek%20votes.%20But%20over%20the%20years%2C%20all%20that%20seems%20to%20have%20disappeared.%20Nobody%20comes%20to%20ask%20for%20votes%20except%20the%20local%20candidates.%20Despite%20this%2C%20I%20wish%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20win%20because%20it%20would%20give%20the%20community%20breathing%20space%20unlike%20the%20current%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F26101250%2F2020_3img24_Mar_2020_PTI24-03-2020_000230B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F26101250%2F2020_3img24_Mar_2020_PTI24-03-2020_000230B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F26101250%2F2020_3img24_Mar_2020_PTI24-03-2020_000230B-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F26101250%2F2020_3img24_Mar_2020_PTI24-03-2020_000230B-1024x682.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-443850%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20CM%20Shivraj%20Singh%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Chouhan%20Kamal%20Nath%20in%20Bhopal.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40ChouhanShivraj%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResidents%20here%20see%20this%20as%20a%20stark%20reflection%20of%20the%20broader%20socio-economic%20challenges%20faced%20by%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state.%20They%20attribute%20these%20circumstances%20to%20the%20neglect%20exhibited%20by%20civic%20authorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShakir%20Ahmed%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20employed%20in%20a%20private%20company%2C%20points%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20political%20leadership%20as%20a%20significant%20factor%20contributing%20to%20the%20poor%20civic%20conditions%20in%20these%20Muslim%20localities.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20literally%20living%20next%20to%20piles%20of%20garbage%20and%20open%20drains%2C%20devoid%20of%20basic%20civic%20amenities%20and%20government%20facilities.%20Municipal%20authorities%20display%20sheer%20negligence%20in%20these%20areas%3B%20their%20garbage%20collection%20vehicles%20seldom%20make%20an%20appearance%20for%20weeks.%20But%20the%20question%20remains%3A%20who%20will%20address%20these%20pressing%20issues%3F%20Unfortunately%2C%20we%20lack%20leaders%20who%20are%20genuinely%20concerned%20about%20the%20daily%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20The%20existing%20leaders%20seem%20more%20preoccupied%20with%20matters%20related%20to%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20neglecting%20the%20essential%20needs%20of%20their%20constituents%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congresss-obc-politics-in-madhya-pradesh-is-to-shivraj-singh-chauhans-benefit%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20High%20Command%20Is%20Alarmed%20by%20MP%20CM%20Shivraj%20Blowing%20Hot%20and%20Cold%20on%20His%20Future%20Plans%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20the%20state%20capital%2C%20social%20scientists%20Christopher%20Jaffrelot%20and%20Shazia%20Aziz%20Wilbers%20state%20in%20their%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMuslims%20in%20Indian%20Cities%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20before%201947%2C%20Bhopal%20was%20a%20significant%20Muslim%20state%2C%20second%20only%20to%20Hyderabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu-Muslim%20relations%20were%20complex%2C%20but%20the%20city%20remained%20peaceful.%20Post-independence%2C%20the%20Muslim%20elite%20struggled%20with%20changing%20political%20dynamics.%20The%20city%20modernised%20without%20their%20full%20participation%2C%20leading%20to%20social%20withdrawal.%20The%201992%20riots%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20BJP%20exacerbated%20tensions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExperts%20point%20out%20that%20Muslims%20face%20similar%20ghettoisation%20and%20marginalisation%20in%20other%20cities%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20pattern%20of%20marginalisation%20within%20the%20city%20is%20not%20confined%20to%20Bhopal%20but%20is%20present%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20too%2C%20such%20as%20Indore%2C%20Burhanpur%2C%20or%20elsewhere.%20Muslims%20continue%20to%20live%20within%20pockets%20of%20the%20cities%20and%20are%20deprived%20of%20basic%20infrastructure%20and%20civic%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shamshur%20Rahman%20Alvi%2C%20a%20veteran%20journalist%20and%20keen%20observer%20of%20minority%20issues%2C%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Alvi%2C%20the%20recent%20upsurge%20in%20hate%20crimes%20against%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fkhargone-madhya-pradesh-communal-tensions-boycott%23%3A~%3Atext%3DKhargone%2520(Madhya%2520Pradesh)%253A%2520On%2Cmoved%2520down%2520the%2520same%2520path.%5C%22%3Ecommunal%20violence%20in%20Khargone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20demolition%20of%20houses%2C%20and%20numerous%20instances%20of%20lynchings%2C%20has%20not%20only%20exposed%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20Muslim%20leadership%20but%20has%20also%20highlighted%20the%20desire%20among%20the%20youth%20to%20exercise%20political%20agency%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Congress%20is%20leaning%20towards%20appeasing%20the%20majority.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYouth%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20are%20becoming%20disenchanted%20with%20secular%20parties%20because%20they%20are%20not%20addressing%20their%20concerns%20and%20aspirations.%20These%20young%20people%20expect%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20speak%20out%20against%20hate%20crimes%20targeting%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20Unfortunately%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20leaders%20from%20secular%20parties%20have%20maintained%20strategic%20silence%20on%20these%20issues%2C%20fearing%20it%20might%20upset%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20majority.%20This%20trend%20has%20sparked%20debates%20about%20representation%20and%20political%20agency%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alvi%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F08143439%2Fimage-127.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F08143439%2Fimage-127.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F08143439%2Fimage-127-300x132.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F08143439%2Fimage-127-1024x449.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-600489%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20photo%20of%20district%20authorities%20demolishing%2012%20shops%20belonging%20to%20Talab%20Chowk%20Masjid%20committee%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20riots%20in%20Khargone.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETwo%20main%20reasons%20behind%20poor%20Muslim%20representation%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitical%20stakeholders%20and%20activists%20in%20the%20state%20believe%20that%20poor%20Muslim%20representation%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20two%20significant%20factors%3A%20the%20polarisation%20of%20votes%20after%20the%20Babri%20Mosque%20demolition%20in%201992%20and%20the%20division%20of%20the%20Muslim%20population%20due%20to%20the%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%20in%202002%20during%20the%20Congress%20rule.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMohammad%20Mahir%2C%20who%20runs%20Muslim%20Vikas%20Parishad%20points%20out%20that%20historically%20there%20has%20always%20been%20a%20two-party%20game%20in%20the%20state%2C%20BJP%20vs%20Congress%2C%20and%20this%20has%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20enabling%20majoritarian%20politics%20and%20ensuring%20upper%20caste%20domination%20in%20electoral%20politics%2C%20unlike%20states%20where%20politics%20of%20social%20justice%20unfolded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20politics%20has%20traditionally%20revolved%20around%20communalism%20and%20secularism%2C%20with%20little%20emphasis%20on%20representation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahir%20stated.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20lack%20of%20focus%20on%20representation%20allowed%20dominant%20groups%20to%20maintain%20their%20participation.%20Another%20significant%20factor%20is%20the%20trend%20among%20secular%20parties%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Congress%20in%20MP%2C%20where%20non-Muslim%20leaders%20vie%20for%20tickets%20in%20Muslim-dominated%20constituencies.%20They%20perceive%20it%20as%20an%20easy%20win%20as%20Muslims%20are%20considered%20their%20natural%20voters.%20This%20trend%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20despite%20the%20influence%20Muslims%20hold%20in%20at%20least%2020%20seats%2C%20only%20two%20tickets%20were%20allocated%20to%20Muslim%20candidates%20in%20the%20last%20election%2C%20both%20from%20Bhopal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMahir%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20Vikas%20Parishad%20has%20submitted%20a%2015-point%20memorandum%2C%20to%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20addressing%20concerns%20related%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20They%20have%20demanded%20that%20these%20parties%20include%20these%20points%20in%20their%20respective%20manifestos.%20Some%20of%20these%20demands%20include%20allowing%20students%20to%20seek%20education%20in%20their%20mother%20tongue%2C%20implementing%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdalit-muslims-christians-reservation-supreme-court-centre%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERanganathan%20Misra%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ECommission%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20pertaining%20to%20the%20community%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.newsnationtv.com%2Fcities%2Fbhopal%2Fmp-govt-delaying-setting-up-amu-bhopal-campus-16624.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estarting%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAMU%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20campus%20in%20the%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Alvi%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20state%20has%20also%20impacted%20electoral%20demography%20and%20made%20things%20very%20tricky%20for%20Muslims%20politically.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDelimitation%20is%20a%20process%20in%20which%20the%20Boundary%20Committee%20redraws%20the%20boundaries%20of%20various%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%20and%20converts%20seats%20based%20on%20the%20recent%20census.%20The%20present%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%20was%20done%20in%202002%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%202001%20census.%20Constituencies%20such%20as%20Bhopal%2C%20Satna%2C%20Rewa%2C%20Narela%2C%20and%20Jabalpur%20were%20divided%20into%20different%20constituencies%20in%202002%20by%20the%20commission%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%202023%20elections%20are%20concerned%2C%20many%20of%20the%20Muslims%20whom%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20spoke%20to%20found%20themselves%20with%20no%20viable%20choice%20apart%20from%20the%20Congress%20to%20rely%20on%2C%20despite%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20recent%20shift%20toward%20majoritarian%20politics%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPresently%2C%20I%20prefer%20to%20think%20as%20a%20common%20voter%20of%20the%20state%2C%20not%20just%20as%20a%20Muslim.%20It%20is%20clear%20to%20me%2C%20as%20a%20regular%20voter%2C%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20failed%20the%20state%20comprehensively%2C%20be%20it%20in%20healthcare%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20security%2C%20or%20malnutrition.%20It%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20that%2078%2C000%20children%20were%20found%20to%20be%20malnourished%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%20this%20calendar%20year%2C%20the%20state%20government%20had%20said%20in%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarked%20Anas%20Ali%2C%20President%20of%20Barkatullah%20Youth%20Forum.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnas%20also%20emphasised%20that%20there%20is%20a%20concerning%20perception%20that%20Muslims%20are%20being%20deemed%20irrelevant%20and%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20taken%20for%20granted.%20However%2C%20he%20emphasised%20that%20political%20parties%20should%20be%20mindful%20that%20Muslim%20votes%20are%20pivotal%20in%20forming%20a%20government.%20In%20the%20state%2C%20a%20swing%20of%20just%201%20or%202%25%20of%20votes%20can%20significantly%20alter%20the%20political%20landscape%20and%20change%20the%20fate%20of%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202018%2C%20Congress%20had%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2040.89%25%2C%20whereas%20BJP%20had%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2041.02%25.%20Opinion%20polls%20indicate%20a%20difference%20of%201%25%20in%20vote%20share%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20this%20time%20as%20well