%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epostpartum%20depression%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20Shubhrata%20tried%20to%20distract%20herself%20with%20official%20work%20but%20she%20did%20not%20feel%20like%20her%20old%20self%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20days%20when%20I%20could%20not%20get%20out%20of%20bed%20or%20even%20brush%20my%20teeth.%20If%20anyone%20would%20say%20a%20kind%20word%20to%20me%2C%20I%20would%20break%20down.%20Since%20nothing%20was%20physically%20wrong%20with%20me%2C%20I%20could%20not%20understand%20what%20was%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20people%20started%20comparing%20her%20with%20others%20who%20did%20not%20have%20a%20good%20job%20and%20a%20supportive%20family%20like%20hers%20and%20yet%20performed%20better%20than%20Shubhrata.%20This%20would%20stress%20her%20out%20even%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20the%2049-year-old%20experienced%20a%20severe%20panic%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FShubhrata-Prakash-1696943803.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shubhrata%20documented%20her%20struggles%20in%20the%20book%20The%20D%20Word%3A%20A%20Survivor's%20Guide%20to%20Depression.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FShubhrata-Prakash-1696943803.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FShubhrata-Prakash-1696943803-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FShubhrata-Prakash-1696943803-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FShubhrata-Prakash-1696943803-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FShubhrata-Prakash-1696943803-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20