k%20cow%20urine%20and%20then%20enter%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20appalled%20Nikhil%2C%20who%20now%20shares%20that%20Laxmi%20Devi%E2%80%99s%20views%20have%20changed%20since%20then.%20As%20she%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CNikhil%20and%20his%20team%20of%20Planet%20Trotter%20helped%20us%20get%20necessary%20medicines%20and%20pads%20and%20education%20about%20menstruation.%20Now%20we%20buy%20pads%20from%20the%20village%20shop.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENikhil%20and%20his%20team%20frequently%20distribute%20books%20and%20educational%20materials%20to%20students%20of%20the%20government-run%20schools%20in%20all%20three%20villages.%20To%20date%2C%20they%20have%20helped%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20than%20500%20students%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20such%20trip%20in%202019%2C%20Nikhil%20came%20across%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-functional%20computers%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20school%2C%20and%20he%20enquired%20about%20it.%20He%20was%20told%20that%20these%20had%20not%20been%20working%20for%20nine%20years%20as%20the%20electricity%20requirements%20could%20not%20be%20met.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20six%201.5%20kW%20solar%20panels%20installed%20in%20the%20school%20which%20ensure%20the%20smooth%20functioning%20of%20the%20computers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FScreenshot-2022-07-07-155357_11zon-1696939453.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20solar%20panels%20installed%20in%20the%20school%20are%20now%20used%20to%20power%20the%20computers%20that%20lay%20dysfunctional%20for%20years