aborty%20were%20sent%20to%20ten%20days%20of%20judicial%20custody%20in%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20sessions%20judge%20Hardeep%20Kaur%20of%20the%20Patiala%20House%20Courts%20passed%20the%20order%20after%20Purkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty%20were%20produced%20in%20court%20after%20the%20five%20days%20of%20police%20custody%20had%20expired%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fnews-updates%2Fnewsclick-founder-arrest-prabir-purkayastha-judicial-custody-chinese-propaganda-uapa-239778%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20special%20cell%20in%20a%20terror%20case%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelhi-police-terror-fir-against-newsclick-names-chinese-firms-xiaomi-vivo-puts-lawyers-in-crosshairs%5C%22%3Ewhich%20claims%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20received%20Chinese%20funding%20to%20criticise%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20promote%20Chinese%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20public%20prosecutor%20(APP)%20Atul%20Srivastava%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20Delhi%20police%20was%20seeking%20judicial%20custody%20because%20their%20physical%20presence%20is%20not%20required%20at%20this%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPurkayastha%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20Khurana%2C%20opposing%20the%20grant%20of%20judicial%20custody%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbare%20reading%20of%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20FIR%20would%20show%20that%20there%20is%20no%20criminal%20offence%20made%20out%E2%80%9D%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20case%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-case-allegations-uapa-legal-experts%5C%22%3ENewsClick%20Case%3A%20Do%20Allegations%20Justify%20Invoking%20of%20UAPA%3F%20Legal%20Experts%20Weigh%20In.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20allegation%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20used%20any%20bomb%20or%20dynamite%20which%20has%20caused%20loss%20of%20death%20and%20property.%20There%20is%20no%20allegation%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20used%20any%20criminal%20force%20in%20the%20entire%20FIR.%20There%20is%20no%20act%20of%20kidnapping%2C%20detention%20or%20abduction.%20None%20of%20the%20acts%20attributed%20to%20me%20has%20any%20elements%20of%20Section%2015%20of%20UAPA%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhurana%20said%20that%20a%20journalist%20cannot%20be%20punished%20for%20criticising%20the%20government%20in%20power.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fnewsclick-arrests-prabir-purkayastha-amit-chakraborty-remanded-judicial-custody-10-days-delhi-court%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20APP%20Srivastava%20responded%2C%20%E2%80%9CYour%20purpose%20was%20not%20criticising%20(the%20government)%20but%20propagating%20the%20propaganda%20of%20a%20country%20that%20is%20inimical%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhurana%20also%20reiterated%20that%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20not%20received%20any%20money%20from%20China%20and%20all%20investment%20came%20through%20banking%20channels%20and%20was%20duly%20reported%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%2C%20appearing%20for%20NewsClick%E2%80%99s%20HR%20head%20Amit%20Chakraborty%2C%20said%20his%20client%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20not%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR%20as%20an%20accused.%20While%20the%20FIR%20says%20Chakravarti%20owns%20shares%20in%20NewsClick%2C%20his%20holdings%20in%20the%20company%20equal%200.1%25%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20%5Ban%5D%20allegation%20there%20is%20money%20coming%20in%20and%20some%20news%20is%20being%20published%20with%20a%20particular%20agenda.%20I%20have%20not%20been%20involved%20in%20any%20publication.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20journalist%2C%20or%20an%20editor%20or%20writer%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chakravarti%E2%80%99s%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20APP%20Srivastava%20said%20that%20the%20police%20had%20already%20satisfied%20the%20court%20during%20the%20time%20of%20police%20remand%20that%20the%20offences%20were%20made%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20it%20is%20not%20a%20case%20of%20first%20remand.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20first%20remand%2C%20we%20had%20satisfied%20my%20ladyship%20with%20how%20the%20offences%20were%20made%20out%E2%80%A6%20We%20are%20at%20the%20stage%20of%20collecting%20evidence.%20See%20our%20fairness.%20We%20have%20said%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20police%20remand%20as%20of%20now%20and%20will%20ask%20later%20if%20we%20need%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPurkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty%20were%20arrested%20on%20October%203%20and%20were%20remanded%20to%20seven%20days%20of%20police%20custody%20on%20October%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20Monday%20reserved%20its%20order%20in%20the%20pleas%20moved%20by%20Purkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-reserves-judgment-on-pleas-challenging-remand-orders-of-newsclick-editor-hr-head%5C%22%3Echallenging%20the%20trial%20court%E2%80%99s%20remand%20order%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696945833000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F10124838%2Fp-house-court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnewsclick-case-purkayasthan-chakravarti-10-days-judicial-custody%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20police%20told%20the%20court%20that%20it%20was%20seeking%20judicial%20custody%20because%20their%20physical%20presence%20is%20not%20required%20at%20this%20stage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnewsclick-case-purkayasthan-chakravarti-10-days-judicial-custody%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20LG%20Grants%20Sanction%20to%20Prosecute%20Arundhati%20Roy%20in%202010%20'Provocative%20Speeches'%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2F15161252%2FArundhati_Roy__Man_Booker_Prize_winner.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EDelhi%20lieutenant%20governor%20V.K.%20Saxena%20has%20accorded%20sanction%20for%20the%20prosecution%20of%20author%20Arundhati%20Roy%20and%20retired%20Kashmir%20professor%20Sheikh%20Showkat%20Hussain%20in%20connection%20with%20a%202010%20case%20accusing%20them%20of%20making%20provocative%20speeches%20that%20called%20for%20separation%20of%20Kashmir%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20note%2C%20Saxena%20has%20noted%20that%20a%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%20is%20made%20out%20against%20Roy%20and%20Hussain%20for%20the%20commission%20of%20offences%20under%20Sections%20153A%2C%20153B%20and%20505%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20for%20their%20speeches%20at%20a%20public%20function%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20While%20Section%20153A%20deals%20with%20offences%20pertaining%20to%20those%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20and%20residence%2C%20Section%20153B%20relates%20to%20offences%20relating%20to%20imputations%2C%20and%20assertions%20prejudicial%20to%20national%20integration.%20Section%20505%20covers%20offences%20relating%20to%20making%20or%20circulation%20of%20false%20statements%2C%20rumours%2C%20or%20information%20with%20a%20specific%20intent%20to%20cause%20mutiny%20or%20fear%20among%20military%20personnel%2C%20inciting%20offences%20against%20the%20state%20or%20public%20tranquility.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sanction%20from%20the%20Delhi%20LG%20was%20necessitated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20initiating%20prosecution%20under%20Sections%20153A%20and%20153B%20requires%20prior%20sanction%20from%20the%20government.%20This%20is%20required%20before%20the%20trial%2C%20and%20not%20at%20the%20stage%20of%20the%20preliminary%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20note%20also%20clarifies%20that%20sanction%20has%20not%20been%20provided%20to%20prosecute%20the%20accused%20under%20sedition%20(Section%20124A)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20IPC%20sections%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR.%20However%2C%20a%20case%20under%20the%20section%20is%20made%20out%2C%20the%20note%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20LG%20was%20constrained%20against%20giving%20sanction%20because%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-puts-sedition-law-in-abeyance-during-government-review%5C%22%3Elandmark%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20directed%20all%20pending%20trials%2C%20appeals%2C%20and%20proceedings%20with%20respect%20to%20charges%20framed%20under%20sedition%20be%20kept%20in%20abeyance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20registered%20on%20November%2029%2C%202010%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20from%20Sushil%20Pandit%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20from%20Kashmir.%20The%20complainant%20said%20speakers%20at%20a%20conference%20organised%20by%20the%20Committee%20for%20Release%20of%20Political%20Prisoners%20(CRPP)%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20%E2%80%98Azadi%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Only%20Way%E2%80%99%20on%20October%2021%2C%202010%20had%20delivered%20%E2%80%9Cprovocative%20speeches%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20also%20called%20for%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cseparation%20of%20Kashmir%20from%20India%E2%80%9D.%20Pandit%20also%20said%20the%20speeches%20were%20provocative%20in%20nature%2C%20thus%20jeopardising%20public%20peace%20and%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20said%20Roy%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9CKashmir%20was%20never%20part%20of%20India%20and%20was%20forcibly%20occupied%20by%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20of%20India%20and%20every%20possible%20effort%20should%20be%20made%20for%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20from%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20%E2%80%93%20Syed%20Ali%20Shah%20Geelani%2C%20a%20Kashmiri%20separatist%20leader%20and%20Syed%20Abdul%20Rahman%20Geelani%2C%20a%20Delhi%20University%20lecturer%20who%20acquitted%20in%20parliament%20attack%20case%20%E2%80%93%20are%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696944911000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2F15161252%2FArundhati_Roy__Man_Booker_Prize_winner.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-lg-grants-sanction-prosecute-arundhati-roy-2010-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20writer-activist%20and%20retired%20professor%20Sheikh%20Showkat%20Hussain%20will%20be%20tried%20for%20promoting%20enmity%20and%20assertions%20prejudicial%20to%20national%20integration.%20Because%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20put%20the%20sedition%20law%20in%20abeyance%2C%20the%20LG%20did%20not%20provide%20sanction%20for%20prosecution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-lg-grants-sanction-prosecute-arundhati-roy-2010-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Despite%20Repeated%20Requests%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Avoids%20Meeting%20Manipur%20BJP%20MLAs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10171456%2FF8Ee91zbUAA-T1C.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnorth-east-india%2Fmanipur%2Fbjp-manipur-unit-writes-nadda-public-anger-8962955%2F%5C%22%3Eletter%20recently%20written%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BJP%E2%80%99s)%20Manipur%20unit%20to%20party%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20has%20come%20into%20national%20focus%20for%20seeking%20his%20intervention%20to%20%E2%80%9Crevoke%20Article%20355%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20violence-hit%20northeastern%20state%2C%20and%20also%20to%20clarify%20%E2%80%9Cif%20there%20is%20anything%20(Article%20355)%20as%20such%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%20The%20letter%20also%20asks%20that%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20be%20restored%20the%20command%20of%20the%20Unified%20Command%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20anger%20and%20protest%E2%80%9D%20is%20being%20directed%20at%20the%20state%20government%20run%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20needs%20highlighting%20is%20that%20the%20state%20unit%20had%20also%20requested%20Nadda%20%E2%80%9Cto%20persuade%E2%80%9D%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%9Cto%20give%20an%20appointment%20to%20the%20joint%20MLAs%E2%80%99%20team%20who%20are%20now%20holding%20up%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20for%20the%20appointment%20in%20the%20letter%20signed%20by%20six%20top%20organisational%20post%20holders%20of%20the%20BJP%20state%20unit%20including%20president%20A.%20Sharda%20Devi%20is%20significant%20considering%20Modi%20has%20not%20only%20refused%20to%20directly%20address%20the%20five-months-long%20violence%20and%20ethnic%20unrest%20in%20the%20state%20ruled%20by%20his%20party%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20affected%20people%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20for%20it%2C%20but%20has%20also%20thus%20far%20not%20given%20an%20audience%20even%20to%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20legislators%20to%20hear%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20various%20times%20since%20the%20violence%20unfolded%20in%20the%20state%20since%20on%20May%203%2C%20MLAs%20from%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20both%20from%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20%E2%80%93%20have%20sought%20appointments%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20have%20an%20audience%20on%20the%20crisis.%20In%20June%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-narendra-modi-silence-mlas-teams%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20least%20three%20such%20delegations%20were%20camping%20in%20New%20Delhi%20seeking%20his%20time%20to%20apprise%20him%20of%20the%20unprecedented%20violence%20being%20faced%20by%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20state%2C%20leading%20to%20death%20and%20injury%20of%20several%20hundreds%20and%20loss%20of%20thousands%20of%20properties%2C%20as%20their%20elected%20representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-September%2C%20a%20delegation%20of%2018%20BJP%20MLAs%20from%20the%20state%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2F18-manipur-mlas-camp-in-delhi-to-push-peace-efforts%2Farticleshow%2F103720528.cms%5C%22%3Ehad%20been%20camping%20in%20the%20capital%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20about%20two%20weeks%20to%20meet%20various%20central%20leaders%20to%20help%20speed%20up%20the%20peace%20efforts%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20delegation%20included%20senior%20party%20leaders%20like%20Yumnam%20Khemchand%20and%20Biswajit%20Singh.%20They%20were%20keen%20to%20have%20an%20audience%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20too%20since%20there%20has%20been%20strong%20discontent%20within%20the%20public%20in%20Manipur%20for%20the%20silence%20being%20maintained%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20Modi%20spoke%20only%20once%20thus%20far%20in%20reference%20to%20a%20horrific%20video%20of%20sexual%20assault%20of%20two%20women%20from%20the%20state%20by%20a%20mob%20but%20not%20without%20citing%20examples%20from%20some%20opposition%20ruled%20states%20for%20lack%20of%20safety%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20unit%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20published%20in%20various%20news%20reports%20on%20September%2030%2C%20was%20to%20seek%20Nadda%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20to%20ensure%20an%20appointment%20of%20the%20delegation%20with%20the%20prime%20minister.%20A%20state%20unit%20office%20bearer%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20today%20that%20the%20delegation%20failed%20to%20meet%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696944643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10171456%2FF8Ee91zbUAA-T1C.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-repeated-requests-pm-modi-avoids-meeting-manipur-bjp-mlas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20various%20times%20since%20the%20violence%20unfolded%20in%20the%20state%20since%20on%20May%203%2C%20MLAs%20from%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20both%20from%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20%E2%80%93%20have%20sought%20appointments%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20have%20an%20audience%20on%20the%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-repeated-requests-pm-modi-avoids-meeting-manipur-bjp-mlas%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kangana%20meets%20the%20only%20female%20Rafale%20fighter%20pilot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696944511000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104319691%2Cimgsize-202162.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftejas-kangana-ranaut-meets-the-first-and-only-female-rafale-fighter-pilot-flight-lieutenant-shivangi-singh-see-pic-inside%2Farticleshow%2F104319711.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104319711.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKangana%20Ranaut%20who%20will%20be%20seen%20playing%20the%20character%20of%20an%20Air%20Force%20fighter%20pilot%20in%20Tejas%20got%20to%20meet%20the%20real-life%20Air%20Force%20Pilot%2C%20Flight%20Lieutenant%20Shivangi%20Singh%2C%20the%20