ogramme.%20In%20the%20same%20post%2C%20she%20mentioned%20that%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20cultural%20similarities%20than%20differences%E2%80%9D%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20media%20reports%20had%20suggested%20that%20her%20exit%20was%20related%20to%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20concerns%E2%80%9D%20following%20a%20complaint%20filed%20in%20Delhi%20by%20a%20lawyer.%20The%20complaint%20filed%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20Vineet%20Jindal%20October%206%20accused%20Abbas%20of%20posting%20%E2%80%9Cderogatory%E2%80%9D%20tweets%20targeting%20the%20Hindu%20faith%2C%20based%20on%20screenshots%20of%20posts%20made%20by%20an%20account%20with%20her%20name%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDated%20October%204%2C%20the%20complaint%20alleged%20that%20Abbas%20had%20made%20statements%20that%20were%20anti-India%20and%20Hinduphobic.%20Jindal%20reported%20the%20complaint%20to%20the%20Cyber%20Cell%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20via%20X%2C%20requesting%20the%20filing%20of%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20against%20Abbas%20under%20Sections%20153A%2C%20295%2C%20506%2C%20121%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%2C%20and%20Section%2067%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%20for%20her%20%E2%80%9Cderogatory%20remarks%20about%20Hinduism%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%20statements%E2%80%9D.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20lawyer%20demanded%20that%20Abbas%20be%20removed%20as%20a%20presenter%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESamaa%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samaa.tv%2F208732344-pakistani-presenter-zainab-abbas-leaves-india-over-safety-concerns%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Abbas%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20maintained%20that%20she%20had%20been%20unjustly%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESports%20and%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPakistani%20fans%20and%20journalists%20have%20been%20facing%20prolonged%20delays%20in%20obtaining%20visas%20to%20attend%20World%20Cup%20matches%20in%20India%2C%20which%20commenced%20last%20week.%20Even%20the%20players%E2%80%99%20visa%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-world-cup-pakistan-board-flags-delay-by-india-in-granting-visas-to-team-with-icc%5C%22%3Egranted%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20after%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20petitioned%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20some%20Pakistan%20citizens%20who%20had%20tickets%20for%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20opening%20game%20against%20the%20Netherlands%20could%20not%20attend%20because%20of%20unresolved%20visa%20issues.%20The%20Indian%20high%20commission%2C%20awaiting%20instructions%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20home%20ministry%2C%20has%20not%20yet%20provided%20a%20response%2C%20leaving%20fans%20anxious%20about%20attending%20future%20matches%2C%20including%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20game%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%2060%20journalists%20from%20Pakistan%20are%20waiting%20to%20get%20a%20visa%20clearance%20from%20Indian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fpakistan-media-fans-still-awaiting-visas-for-world-cup%2Farticle67389744.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESportstar%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20PCB%20source%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTill%20now%20there%20is%20no%20word%20about%20the%20visas%20and%20the%20World%20Cup%20has%20already%20started.%20This%20is%20not%20what%20we%20expected%2C%20but%20we%20are%20still%20hoping%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20clears%20the%20visas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Zaka%20Ashraf%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20PCB%20Interim%20Management%20Committee%2C%20met%20with%20foreign%20secretary%20Syrus%20Sajjad%20Qazi%20to%20express%20concerns%20about%20the%20delayed%20issuance%20of%20visas%20for%20Pakistani%20fans%20and%20journalists%20who%20want%20to%20travel%20to%20India%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReports%20have%20highlighted%20the%20contrasting%20policies%20of%20other%20sports%20events%20like%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20Olympics%2C%20where%20measures%20are%20in%20place%20to%20facilitate%20easy%20entry%20for%20journalists%20and%20fans.%20For%20example%2C%20during%20the%202018%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%2C%20tournament%20host%20Russia%20introduced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.themoscowtimes.com%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2Fworld-cup-fans-granted-visa-free-entry-to-russia-under-newly-passed-bill-a62355%5C%22%3Ea%20visa-free%20entry%3C%2Fa%3E%20policy%20for%20fans%20holding%20tickets.%20Journalists%20were%20promptly%20issued%20visas%20on%20the%20spot%20at%20Russian%20consular%20offices.%20Qatar%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fragomen.com%2Finsights%2Fqatar-relaxed-requirements-for-2022-fifa-world-cup-visas.html%5C%22%3Erelaxed%20visa%20requirements%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20it%20hosted%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20hope%20remains%2C%20with%20speculation%20suggesting%20that%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20Pakistani%20journalists%20might%20receive%20visas%20before%20the%20much-anticipated%20India-Pakistan%20match%20on%20October%2014.%20However%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20response%20from%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20in%20Pakistan%20has%20deepened%20concerns.%20Former%20PCB%20chief%20Ehsan%20Mani%20called%20for%20the%20Pakistani%20team%E2%80%99s%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20World%20Cup%20if%20visas%20are%20not%20issued%20to%20fans%20and%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696941931000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10180840%2FF5-F4WVbUAAAV0z.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-world-cup-pakistani-presenter-zainab-abbas-leaves-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lawyer%20Vineet%20Jindal's%20complaint%20accused%20Zainab%20Abbas%20of%20posting%20%26quot%3Bderogatory%26quot%3B%20tweets%20targeting%20the%20Hindu%