%20%3Cp%3ESources%20privy%20to%20the%20developments%20at%20the%20festival%20said%20that%20activists%20belonging%20to%20right-wing%20organisations%20raised%20objection%20over%20four%20of%20the%20many%20speakers%20who%20were%20invited%20to%20the%20festival.%20The%20objection%20was%20against%20inviting%20journalists%20and%20authors%20like%20Aakar%20Patel%2C%20Josy%20Joseph%2C%20Shruti%20Ganpataye%20and%20Shivam%20Shankar%20Singh%20to%20the%20festival.%20For%20the%20February%202024%20edition%2C%20around%2040%20speakers%20were%20invited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatel%2C%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20recently%20came%20out%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FAakar-Patel%2Fe%2FB075J9J5TN%2Fref%3Ddp_byline_cont_book_1%5C%22%3Ebooks%20that%20focus%20on%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Investigative%20journalist%20and%20author%20Joseph%E2%80%99s%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Silent%20Coup%3A%20A%20History%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Deep%20State%3C%2Fem%3E%20closely%20looks%20at%20bias%20that%20runs%20deep%20in%20the%20Indian%20security%20establishment%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20Ganpatye%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20journalist%2C%20recently%20came%20out%20with%20her%20debut%20book%20%3Cem%3EWho%20Will%20Bell%20The%20Cow%3F%3A%20Beef%20Ban%3A%20Decoding%20its%20cultural%2C%20social%2C%20and%20economical%20aspects%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EHow%20to%20Win%20an%20Indian%20Election%3A%20What%20Political%20Parties%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Want%20You%20to%20Know%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0book%20looks%20at%20political%20campaigns%20and%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20how%20my%20book%20%E2%80%9CWho%20Will%20Bell%20The%20Cow%3F%E2%80%9D%20was%20withdrawn%20for%20Vidarbha%20Lit%20Fest.%20I%20appreciate%20the%20honesty%20of%20the%20organisers%20to%20admit%20the%20pressure%20and%20come%20out%20open%20about%20it.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6vkW9mnaR8%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6vkW9mnaR8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Shruti%20Ganapatye%20(%40shrutiganapatye)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshrutiganapatye%2Fstatus%2F1710952843354738998%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%208%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChaudhary%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20came%20in%20following%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20some%20major%20sponsors%20of%20the%20festival.%20The%20initial%20objection%2C%20Chaudhary%20confirmed%2C%20was%20raised%20against%20more%20than%20four%20speakers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20somehow%20salvaged%20the%20situation%20and%20managed%20to%20convince%20them%20(the%20sponsors).%20But%20they%20refused%20to%20be%20convinced%20about%20the%20four%20important%20speakers%20at%20the%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20Choudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20added%20that%20the%20curators%E2%80%99%20family%20members%20were%20approached%20by%20right-wing%20persons.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20pressure%20was%20built%20from%20different%20sides.%20When%20they%20felt%20we%20might%20not%20budge%20if%20the%20sponsors%20withdrew%20and%20try%20to%20personally%20raise%20funds%2C%20our%20families%20were%20approached%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChaudhary%2C%20Sarda%20and%20Dharamadhikari%20had%20a%20decision%20to%20make.%20Whether%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20independence%20in%20running%20the%20festival%20or%20step%20down.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20that%20we%20found%20ourselves%20in%2C%20only%20the%20latter%20was%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaudhary%20said.%20This%2C%20the%20curators%20say%2C%20happened%20as%20they%20could%20not%20have%20managed%20to%20run%20the%20show%20without%20sponsors%20supporting%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20withdrew%20actually%20were%20funding%20over%2060%25%20of%20the%20total%20budget%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaudhary%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20festival%20idea%20was%20mooted%20to%20focus%20on%20non-fiction%20writers.%20In%202020%20too%2C%20many%20writers%2C%20known%20for%20their%20critical%20take%20on%20the%20current%20dispensation%2C%20were%20invited%20to%20the%20festival.%20%E2%80%9CLike%20say%20Akshaya%20Mukul%20was%20one%20of%20the%20speakers.%20But%20that%20time%2C%20the%20festival%20was%20not%20as%20well%20known.%20It%20was%20our%20first%20attempt%20to%20bring%20writers%20together.%20And%20we%20managed%20without%20any%20pushback%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaudhary%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20who%20exactly%20had%20approached%20them%2C%20their%20families%20or%20the%20sponsors%2C%20Chaudhary%20refused%20to%20name%20names.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20writers%E2%80%99%20community%20is%20very%20small%20here%20in%20Nagpur%20and%20we%20get%20easily%20identified%20and%20targeted.%20It%20has%20taken%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20courage%20to%20publicly%20announce%20that%20we%20have%20stepped%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696941033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F10163925%2Fbanner-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fvidarbha-literary-festival-curators-organiser-step-down-after-right-wing-threats%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sources%20privy%20to%20the%20developments%20at%20the%20festival%20said%20that%20activists%20belonging%20to%20right-wing%20organisations%20raised%20objection%20over%20four%20of%20the%20many%20speakers%20who%20were%20invited%20to%20the%20festival.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fvidarbha-literary-festival-curators-organiser-step-down-after-right-wing-threats%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rakul%20Preet%20Singh's%20vacation%20postcards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696941000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104314181%2Cim