20free%20expression%20and%20democratic%20rights%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20imposition%20of%20severe%20restrictions%20on%20the%20independent%20media%20and%20media%20professionals%20by%20governments%20has%20become%20a%20recurring%20feature%20of%20the%20continuing%20crisis%20of%20democracy%20in%20South%20Asia.%20The%20unending%20assault%20on%20free%20expression%20and%20democratic%20rights%20in%20South%20Asia%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20country-specific%20development.%20Neither%20is%20it%20confined%20to%20specific%20nation%20states.%20Rather%20it%20is%20a%20regional%20phenomenon%2C%20signalling%20a%20new%20and%20worsening%20phase%20of%20democratic%20backsliding%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recent%20raids%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%2046%20houses%20of%20journalists%20connected%20with%20the%20Indian%20news%20portal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20illustrates%20this%20shocking%20trend.%20More%20unsettling%20is%20the%20arrest%20of%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20its%20Editor-in-Chief%2C%20and%20Amith%20Chakravorty%2C%20its%20Head%20of%20Human%20Resources%2C%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20investigating%20them%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterror%20case%20with%20Chinese%20links%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Indian%20media%20has%20reported%20that%20the%20police%20has%20blatantly%20disregarded%20the%20legally%20sanctioned%20procedures%20in%20arresting%20the%20senior%20journalist%20and%20his%20colleague.%C2%A0%20The%20authorities%20are%20yet%20to%20make%20known%20any%20material%20on%20the%20website%20with%20links%20to%20any%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%20activity%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CChinese%20propaganda%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20join%20the%20progressive%20media%2C%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20activists%20in%20India%20to%20condemn%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20this%20brazen%20attack%20by%20the%20government%20on%20the%20free%20media.%20Harassment%20an