%2Fgeneva-convention-relative-protection-civilian-persons-time-war%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUnited%20Nations%20statutes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20collective%20punishment%20of%20a%20civilian%20population%20is%20considered%20a%20war%20crime.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20siege%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F10%2Fhamas-says-will-kill-hostages-if-israeli-attacks-on-gaza-civilians-continue%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHamas%20has%20threatened%20to%20kill%20Israeli%20hostages%20without%20warning%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20militant%20group%20has%20taken%20at%20least%20150%20Israelis%20hostage%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20the%20attacks%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%20Refugees%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2Fresources%2Freports%2Funrwa-situation-report-3-situation-gaza-strip%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E(UNRWA)%20said%20almost%20190%2C000%20people%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Gaza%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20the%20number%20is%20expected%20to%20increase%20as%20violence%20continues.%20Hospitals%20in%20the%20territory%20are%20overwhelmed%20with%20dead%20and%20wounded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Palestinian%20ministry%20of%20health%20said%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moh.gov.ps%2Fportal%2Fpress-release-issued-by-the-ministry-of-health-oct-9-2023%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20issued%20Monday%20that%20there%20is%20not%20enough%20electricity%20to%20operate%20the%20healthcare%20system%20and%20that%20seven%20hospitals%20and%20health%20centers%20were%20targeted%20and%20damaged.%20The%20ministry%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2023%2F10%2F10%2Fisrael-hamas-war-live-appeals-for-safe-corridor-gaza-toll-goes-past-700%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Csafe%20corridor%20to%20ensure%20the%20entry%20of%20urgent%20medical%20aid%E2%80%9D%20into%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20hospitals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESt%C3%A9phane%20Dujarric%2C%20spokesman%20for%20the%20UN%20secretary-general%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2023%2F10%2F1142077%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20currently%2C%20the%20Gaza%20Power%20Plant%20is%20the%20only%20source%20of%20electricity%20and%20it%20could%20run%20out%20of%20fuel%20within%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUN%20food%20distribution%20centres%20in%20Gaza%20have%20also%20been%20forced%20to%20remain%20closed%2C%20meaning%20many%20civilians%20in%20the%20territory%20have%20not%20received%20food%20rations%20this%20week%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UNRWA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Union%20initially%20suspended%20aid%20to%20Palestine%20and%20then%20backtracked%20on%20the%20announcement%2C%20after%20member%20countries%20complained%20the%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20executive%20had%20overstepped%20the%20mark%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fgermany-austria-suspend-bilateral-aid-palestinians-after-hamas-attack-2023-10-09%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%20over%202%20million%20Palestinians%20residing%20in%20Gaza%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67051292%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E80%25%20rely%20on%20humanitarian%20aid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20residents%20said%20aid%20has%20not%20reached%20the%20enclave%20since%20Saturday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F07%2Fmiddleeast%2Fsirens-israel-rocket-attack-gaza-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%